nl.kb.xml.transformassert

Class TransformAssertWithTransformResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.kb.xml.transformassert.TransformAssertWithTransformResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransformResults

    public class TransformAssertWithTransformResult
extends Object
implements TransformResults
    An instance of this class is returned by TransformAssertWithTransformer.whenTransforming(File, String...)

    It exposes methods to do assertions on the contents of the output of the XSLT under test
